yle="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages" data-ratio="0.6361323155216285" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://2-im.guokr.com/QuErh-oNY_0KNUu0kjJYy9CiaBFjJlcnBPhof8diLUMSAwAA9AEAAFBO.png" data-type="png" data-w="786" style="" src="https://2-im.guokr.com/QuErh-oNY_0KNUu0kjJYy9CiaBFjJlcnBPhof8diLUMSAwAA9AEAAFBO.png?imageView2/1/w/555/h/353"></p><section style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><strong style='color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;'> </strong><br></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);white-space: normal;text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><section style='font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;'><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong data-darkmode-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(25, 25, 25)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-darkmode-bgcolor="rgb(36, 36, 36)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor="rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span data-darkmode-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(0, 122, 170)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(0, 122, 170)" data-darkmode-color-15979270942944="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-darkmode-original-color-15979270942944="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-darkmode-bgcolor="rgb(0, 122, 170)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor="rgb(0, 122, 170)" data-darkmode-color="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-darkmode-original-color="rgb(255, 255, 255)" style="background-color: rgb(0, 122, 170);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> 1 </span></strong></span><strong style='color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;'></strong></section><section style='font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;white-space: normal;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;'><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong data-darkmode-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(25, 25, 25)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-darkmode-bgcolor="rgb(36, 36, 36)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor="rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span data-darkmode-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(25, 25, 25)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor-15979270942944="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-darkmode-color-15979270942944="rgb(0, 122, 170)" data-darkmode-original-color-15979270942944="rgb(0, 122, 170)" data-darkmode-bgcolor="rgb(36, 36, 36)" data-darkmode-original-bgcolor="rgb(255, 255, 255)" data-darkmode-color="rgb(21, 189, 255)" data-darkmode-original-color="rgb(0, 122, 170)" data-style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);">早期阅读不等于早期识字</span></strong></span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><strong> </strong></span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">爸爸妈妈们都希望孩子能早点开始自主阅读，但是，</span><span style="color: rgb(28, 114, 49);"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;">“自主阅读”不能简单地从字面上理解为“自己看书”</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">——让孩子早早地进行识字训练，然后就丢给他一本书“好了，自己去读吧！”并不等于自主阅读。</span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"> </span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;font-family: DengXian;">阅读的最终目的是理解，是从书中领会到作者的意图，提取到有用的信息，并把它们运用到生活和学习中去。</span></strong></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 16px;font-family: DengXian;">阅读理解的过程是对话式的、互动的，也是策略性的，不是机械地把字读出来，而是</span><span style="color: rgb(28, 114, 49);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: DengXian;">要分析文本、消化文本，使其成为自己知识体系的一部分</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: DengXian;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">。</span></strong></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"> </span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">孩子们不认识但却能听懂的字词，同样是词汇量的一部分。</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;"><strong>即使不认字，他们也可以在大人阅读的过程中主动思考、提出问题，和书里的人物互动，真正理解一本书——这才是自主阅读强调的能力。</strong></span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;"></span><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">只不过，我们大人作为有经验的读者，通常会认为这是理所当然的，忽略掉自己在阅读的过程中使用过的一些技能……</span></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></section><section style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><img class="rich_pages" data-ratio="0.6325459317585301" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://2-im.guokr.com/JcLirDGCRqmIJJqwAJ7Tuk3ZNbqxhLozsqkeUGpot3j6AgAA4gEAAFBO.png" data-type="png" data-w="762" style="" src="https://2-im.guokr.com/JcLirDGCRqmIJJqwAJ7Tuk3ZNbqxhLozsqkeUGpot3j6AgAA4gEAAFBO.png?imageView2/1/w/555/h/351"></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"></span><br></section><section style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);text-align: justify;white-space: normal;letter-spac